title: Southwood Apartments Has Availability
posting_body: ['Welcome home!', 'Schedule a Tour!', 'Book an appointment online at 2tour.site/OI4/NJRO', 'Southwood Apartments is located only minutes to major freeways and the airport.', 'Enjoy a smoke-free community featuring landscaped grounds with outdoor grilling spaces, a playground, elevator, and heated underground parking is also available.', 'Dogs and cats are welcome and fiber-optic internet service is available!', 'We have professional on-site management and maintenance.', 'Visit today and see why you will love to call Southwood home!', 'Home Amenities', 'Fiber-optic internet service available', 'Wall air conditioning', 'Balcony or patio options', 'Window coverings', 'Extra storage space available', 'Ceiling fan', 'Walk-in closet', 'Community Amenities', 'Pet friendly - some restrictions apply', 'Elevator access', 'Trash chutes', 'Laundry facility', 'Fitness center', 'Business center', 'Media center', 'Off street parking', 'Playground', 'BBQ & picnic area', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Car wash station', 'Southwood Apartments Information', 'Address:', '10120 Lyndale Cir S, Bloomington MN, 55420', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Details/?pid=25', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Application Fee:', '$45', 'Pet Deposit:', '$300 - 400 (Note: $100 non-refundable)', 'Office Hours', 'Monday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Tuesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Wednesday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Thursday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Friday:', '9:00AM - 6:00PM', 'Saturday:', 'Closed', 'Sunday:', 'Closed']
